1
00:00:00,470 --> 00:00:02,410
(All characters, locations,
organizations, and incidents...)

2
00:00:02,410 --> 00:00:03,710
(in this drama are fictional.)

3
00:00:03,710 --> 00:00:05,180
(This production followed
all guidelines for young actors.)

4
00:00:10,720 --> 00:00:13,350
It's not bad.
A little unoriginal, though.

5
00:00:28,430 --> 00:00:30,030
I'll have to make this mine.

6
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,770
(The misdeeds
of Plagiarist Designer Joo Young Chae...)

7
00:00:32,770 --> 00:00:33,770
(have been exposed.
Read the articles.)

8
00:00:40,780 --> 00:00:42,180
(Episode 92)

9
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:45,750
- Joo Young Chae!
- I can't stand you! Get out!

10
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:49,120
- You fix this.
- Fix what? Everyone at work saw it!

11
00:00:49,190 --> 00:00:51,560
So you just run away?
What are you, a kid?

12
00:00:52,460 --> 00:00:54,730
You're a grown woman.
Start taking some responsibility.

13
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:56,530
This is Cha Jung Won's doing!

14
00:00:56,530 --> 00:00:57,930
It's a trap she set for me!

15
00:00:58,000 --> 00:00:59,400
Don't take her side and lecture me.

16
00:00:59,400 --> 00:01:02,230
Why do you still feel the need
to copy Jung Won's designs?

17
00:01:02,700 --> 00:01:04,400
Aren't you ashamed of yourself?

18
00:01:06,170 --> 00:01:09,340
I will investigate this by the book.
Go home until we have the results.

19
00:01:11,010 --> 00:01:12,180
Am I a criminal now?

20
00:01:12,240 --> 00:01:14,780
Stop being ridiculous.
This isn't your playground.

21
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,750
You will accept whatever action
is taken.

22
00:01:19,750 --> 00:01:23,720
Results, my foot.
And "by the book"? Unbelievable!

23
00:01:27,860 --> 00:01:29,960
(Vice President Jin Se Hoon)

24
00:01:30,630 --> 00:01:32,400
What's wrong with Joo Young Chae?

25
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:35,300
This is just great.

26
00:01:36,130 --> 00:01:39,540
Kunhyang's daughter-in-law
plays childish games at work.

27
00:01:39,770 --> 00:01:41,410
She has completely disgraced me.

28
00:01:41,410 --> 00:01:42,710
More than you have?

29
00:01:43,410 --> 00:01:44,410
What did you say?

30
00:01:44,410 --> 00:01:47,350
No matter how much she messed up,

31
00:01:47,610 --> 00:01:50,220
it's better than you parading around
like a murderer for all to see.

32
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:52,380
You can't even control your wife.
Who are you to lecture me?

33
00:01:52,450 --> 00:01:54,450
I'm nowhere near as bad as you.

34
00:01:54,520 --> 00:01:56,820
- Why, you little...
- Let's use our words.

35
00:01:58,620 --> 00:01:59,860
Don't defend him.

36
00:02:00,260 --> 00:02:01,390
This brat needs to be taught
a lesson.

37
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:02,590
Go on, hit me.

38
00:02:02,730 --> 00:02:04,160
You must hate me
since I'm not your real son.

39
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:06,060
Se Hoon, that's enough!

40
00:02:06,060 --> 00:02:07,770
Look at you, playing peacemaker.

41
00:02:08,030 --> 00:02:09,070
It's all an act.

42
00:02:09,070 --> 00:02:11,340
Young Chae ruined
Kunhyang's fashion show.

43
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:13,340
This isn't something
we can just let slide.

44
00:02:13,400 --> 00:02:16,370
Don't use this as an excuse
to go after Young Chae.

45
00:02:16,910 --> 00:02:19,210
Because in this family,
only Young Chae is on my side.

46
00:02:19,280 --> 00:02:21,210
This isn't about emotions.

47
00:02:21,580 --> 00:02:23,150
It was a formal event.

48
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:25,120
Kunhyang's name was on that show.

49
00:02:25,120 --> 00:02:26,720
I'll use the proper channels
to deal with this.

50
00:02:36,790 --> 00:02:39,930
This is all your fault!
You've ruined me!

51
00:02:40,270 --> 00:02:41,630
You just couldn't stop yourself,
could you?

52
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,670
Did you think you were allowed
to do such things?

53
00:02:44,170 --> 00:02:46,940
Did you really think
that you could just steal my work...

54
00:02:47,140 --> 00:02:48,970
and that I was just your puppet?

55
00:02:49,040 --> 00:02:52,080
Right. Who do you think you are,
being better than me?

56
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:54,050
Why do you have to outshine me?

57
00:02:54,180 --> 00:02:56,880
How can a nobody act so big?

58
00:02:56,950 --> 00:02:58,720
Who do you think you are?

59
00:03:01,220 --> 00:03:02,290
Young Chae.

60
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,220
You've become a real-life Ripley.

61
00:03:06,190 --> 00:03:09,160
- Ripley?
- You still won't acknowledge me.

62
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:12,260
No, you don't want to
acknowledge me.

63
00:03:12,730 --> 00:03:14,570
Why can't you accept someone else
as a designer...

64
00:03:14,630 --> 00:03:16,800
when you know they're more talented
than you?

65
00:03:17,470 --> 00:03:21,370
And why can't you accept
I'm the eldest daughter of Kunhyang?

66
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:23,510
- Why?
- Because you...

67
00:03:24,680 --> 00:03:26,640
were always supposed
to be my servant,

68
00:03:26,910 --> 00:03:28,450
my little shadow!

69
00:03:28,680 --> 00:03:29,750
A part of me feels guilty,

70
00:03:30,680 --> 00:03:33,420
thinking I'm the reason
you've become like this.

71
00:03:34,490 --> 00:03:35,820
If it weren't for me,

72
00:03:36,150 --> 00:03:37,690
you wouldn't have ended up
like this.

73
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:41,360
If I could turn back time, I would.

74
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:45,400
Hey.

75
00:03:46,860 --> 00:03:48,370
Do you feel sorry for me?

76
00:03:49,970 --> 00:03:51,040
How dare you?

77
00:03:51,370 --> 00:03:53,100
Take a good look in the mirror.

78
00:03:53,770 --> 00:03:56,070
See how pathetic you've become.

79
00:03:56,440 --> 00:04:00,980
See how worthless everything
you're clinging to is.

80
00:04:01,350 --> 00:04:02,480
Wake up.

81
00:04:02,610 --> 00:04:03,780
Shut up...

82
00:04:04,180 --> 00:04:05,720
before I kill you.

83
00:04:06,150 --> 00:04:07,790
I said shut up!

84
00:04:16,860 --> 00:04:19,360
Manager Hwang, please continue
to look out for Jung Won.

85
00:04:19,430 --> 00:04:21,670
She's already doing a fine job
on her own.

86
00:04:21,930 --> 00:04:24,900
I think Directors Jung and Park
will be on our side soon.

87
00:04:25,370 --> 00:04:26,740
We can't let our guard down yet.

88
00:04:27,340 --> 00:04:29,110
As long as Se Hoon
is the heir apparent,

89
00:04:29,440 --> 00:04:31,180
they'll ultimately side with him.

90
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:34,110
Vice President Jin's supporters
won't be swayed easily.

91
00:04:34,780 --> 00:04:36,810
They'll see this as their chance.

92
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:40,050
It's time to drop the bomb.

93
00:04:41,120 --> 00:04:43,820
That Se Hoon isn't
Jin Tae Seok's biological son.

94
00:04:44,420 --> 00:04:47,660
We have to show them
they're backing the wrong horse.

95
00:04:47,730 --> 00:04:49,390
That will definitely have
a huge impact.

96
00:04:50,700 --> 00:04:53,530
If it's from me, they'll just say
I'm trying to protect my position.

97
00:04:54,800 --> 00:04:56,530
Manager Hwang,

98
00:04:57,100 --> 00:04:58,100
I need your help.

99
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,580
What am I going to do?

100
00:05:07,350 --> 00:05:09,350
How can I ever show my face
in public again?

101
00:05:10,380 --> 00:05:11,820
Well, the other shoe finally dropped.

102
00:05:11,980 --> 00:05:13,650
This is giving me a headache.

103
00:05:13,790 --> 00:05:15,650
I should've been at the show.

104
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:19,490
So what if you were there?
Would that undo what she did?

105
00:05:20,460 --> 00:05:22,660
You're nothing but trouble.

106
00:05:22,660 --> 00:05:24,800
Why do you always
seek out trouble...

107
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:27,130
and get into every kind
of mess imaginable?

108
00:05:28,270 --> 00:05:31,970
If you're going to do wrong,
be smart enough not to get caught!

109
00:05:32,040 --> 00:05:35,810
"I stole Cha Jung Won's design book,
copied everything,"

110
00:05:35,870 --> 00:05:38,740
"and then I pinned it all
on Jin Se Mi."

111
00:05:38,810 --> 00:05:40,750
You announced it to the whole world!

112
00:05:40,810 --> 00:05:42,310
How am I supposed to cover that up?

113
00:05:42,580 --> 00:05:44,850
You said you could do anything, Mom!

114
00:05:45,050 --> 00:05:46,550
You made a murder charge go away.

115
00:05:46,620 --> 00:05:48,520
Same thing with
Chairman Jin Tae Seok.

116
00:05:49,220 --> 00:05:50,520
So make this go away for me, too.

117
00:05:50,590 --> 00:05:53,190
I'm washing my hands of you!
You ungrateful brat!

118
00:05:55,290 --> 00:05:57,660
This isn't something
you can dismiss so easily.

119
00:06:00,100 --> 00:06:01,570
Se Hoon.

120
00:06:02,930 --> 00:06:05,200
Don't worry. I'll take care of it.

121
00:06:08,570 --> 00:06:09,570
Chairman Gong.

122
00:06:10,110 --> 00:06:11,580
We need to talk.

123
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:17,250
You're aware of what the directors
are up to, right?

124
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:19,950
That they want to oust
Chairman Han Hye Ra?

125
00:06:20,550 --> 00:06:23,860
Their reasons are weak.
It's just a flimsy excuse.

126
00:06:23,920 --> 00:06:25,390
Our company's image is
in the gutter,

127
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:26,790
and our stocks have bottomed out.

128
00:06:27,190 --> 00:06:29,130
There's no way to stop it now.

129
00:06:29,760 --> 00:06:31,930
I'm telling you,
replacing her is the only solution.

130
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,930
And who do you want
to replace her with?

131
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,600
You want the position for yourself,
don't you?

132
00:06:36,670 --> 00:06:40,100
This is
where you need to support me.

133
00:06:40,370 --> 00:06:41,640
And if I do?

134
00:06:42,770 --> 00:06:43,840
Young Chae...

135
00:06:44,280 --> 00:06:45,810
has her flaws,
and she's far from perfect,

136
00:06:46,180 --> 00:06:48,080
but I will take responsibility
for her for the rest of my life.

137
00:06:49,150 --> 00:06:52,120
What? Young Chae has flaws
and is not perfect?

138
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:55,920
Look who's talking.
You're a pathetic loser.

139
00:06:58,390 --> 00:07:01,260
As they say,
a mother is at her daughter's mercy.

140
00:07:03,530 --> 00:07:06,330
I'll give it some serious thought.

141
00:07:06,830 --> 00:07:10,130
For Young Chae's sake,
is there anything I wouldn't do?

142
00:07:10,470 --> 00:07:13,340
I'm counting on you, Chairman Gong.

143
00:07:15,010 --> 00:07:16,970
(Kunhyang Group)

144
00:07:19,710 --> 00:07:21,110
The board meeting is about to start.

145
00:07:21,750 --> 00:07:23,610
I thought Director Kim
would be with you.

146
00:07:23,980 --> 00:07:25,180
Why did you come alone?

147
00:07:27,250 --> 00:07:28,690
I'm starting to feel
a little left out.

148
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:33,860
Vice President Jin,
I've heard a strange rumor.

149
00:07:34,290 --> 00:07:35,360
What kind of rumor?

150
00:07:35,730 --> 00:07:37,360
That you're not...

151
00:07:37,360 --> 00:07:41,300
Chairman Jin Tae Seok's biological son.

152
00:07:41,300 --> 00:07:42,370
Is that true?

153
00:07:43,670 --> 00:07:45,440
Who's spreading
such ridiculous nonsense?

154
00:07:45,870 --> 00:07:47,100
So it's not true?

155
00:07:48,470 --> 00:07:50,640
I don't know
where you heard that from,

156
00:07:51,110 --> 00:07:52,110
but it's absolutely not true.

157
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:54,950
People are saying
they've even seen DNA test results,

158
00:07:55,150 --> 00:07:58,420
and Vice Chairman Joo now owns
over ten percent of the shares,

159
00:07:58,680 --> 00:08:00,120
making him a major shareholder.

160
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:02,190
Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul?

161
00:08:02,250 --> 00:08:05,720
Even your supporters on the board
are starting to waver.

162
00:08:07,460 --> 00:08:09,790
They're worried that
if they support you,

163
00:08:09,990 --> 00:08:11,860
they'll be left high and dry.

164
00:08:11,960 --> 00:08:15,170
- Everyone is incredibly anxious.
- Don't be ridiculous!

165
00:08:15,500 --> 00:08:17,770
I am Jin Se Hoon,
the heir to Kunhyang.

166
00:08:18,100 --> 00:08:20,170
Who would dare doubt me?

167
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,140
(Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

168
00:08:31,750 --> 00:08:33,220
What's all this about,
Vice President Jin?

169
00:08:35,550 --> 00:08:36,650
Joo Ha Neul. It was you, wasn't it?

170
00:08:37,090 --> 00:08:38,890
You're the one spreading rumors
about me, aren't you?

171
00:08:40,560 --> 00:08:43,860
- What are you talking about?
- After pretending to be a saint,

172
00:08:44,160 --> 00:08:45,600
and then you go
and expose my weakness?

173
00:08:45,660 --> 00:08:47,730
You just jump to conclusions
and blame me?

174
00:08:47,930 --> 00:08:50,570
If it comes out that I'm not
Jin Tae Seok's biological son,

175
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,870
who has the most to gain?
It's you, isn't it?

176
00:08:53,940 --> 00:08:56,870
Do you think the board supports you
just because you're his son?

177
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:58,640
If it weren't for that,

178
00:08:59,340 --> 00:09:00,580
then what are you? A figurehead?

179
00:09:00,950 --> 00:09:03,180
Earn their respect with your skills,
Jin Se Hoon.

180
00:09:03,950 --> 00:09:05,250
Joo Ha Neul, do you think...

181
00:09:05,720 --> 00:09:08,450
- you got here on merit?
- You think I didn't?

182
00:09:08,650 --> 00:09:10,890
You're the one who's gunning
for the chairman's seat.

183
00:09:11,190 --> 00:09:14,990
You secretly amassed over
ten percent of Kunhyang's shares?

184
00:09:16,830 --> 00:09:19,760
The Vice Chairman of Kunhyang Group
bought the company's shares.

185
00:09:19,760 --> 00:09:20,800
What's the big deal?

186
00:09:21,330 --> 00:09:22,530
Stop being unreasonable.

187
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:25,500
You act all nice and righteous
on the outside,

188
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,240
but you're just a coward.

189
00:09:27,440 --> 00:09:29,170
I'm sick of feeling sorry for you.

190
00:09:29,610 --> 00:09:31,780
And I'm sick of putting up
with your whining.

191
00:09:32,880 --> 00:09:35,410
Forget whose son you are
or what your background is.

192
00:09:35,780 --> 00:09:37,080
Let's settle this
without our titles.

193
00:09:38,320 --> 00:09:40,320
- What?
- That's right.

194
00:09:40,820 --> 00:09:42,750
I'm going for the chairman's seat
at Kunhyang Group.

195
00:09:43,050 --> 00:09:44,690
So your true colors are showing.

196
00:09:44,690 --> 00:09:45,790
No.

197
00:09:46,720 --> 00:09:49,190
I've always looked ahead
and forged my own path.

198
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:53,030
But you were always looking back,
afraid they'd block your path.

199
00:09:53,100 --> 00:09:56,100
That's because you
were always the one in my way.

200
00:09:57,970 --> 00:09:59,900
If you want to be the best,

201
00:10:00,370 --> 00:10:04,180
stop worrying about me catching up
and just focus on your own path.

202
00:10:04,310 --> 00:10:05,780
And before you know it,

203
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,580
you might just be sitting
in the chairman's seat at Kunhyang.

204
00:10:09,780 --> 00:10:10,980
Got it, Jin Se Hoon?

205
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:13,180
I'll shut that mouth of yours
soon enough.

206
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:15,320
As the chairman.

207
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,830
I have to defeat you, Jin Se Hoon,

208
00:10:29,070 --> 00:10:30,900
so I can finally take down
Jin Tae Seok.

209
00:10:34,140 --> 00:10:35,740
What am I going to do?

210
00:10:36,610 --> 00:10:41,010
Should I follow Han Hye Ra's plan?
Or...

211
00:10:41,080 --> 00:10:42,810
For Young Chae,
this is your chance...

212
00:10:42,810 --> 00:10:45,620
to help Vice President Jin Se Hoon
become the chairman.

213
00:10:46,350 --> 00:10:47,390
You idiot!

214
00:10:48,590 --> 00:10:50,490
You joined Ha Neul's plan
to buy up the shares, didn't you?

215
00:10:50,990 --> 00:10:53,390
But because you're head over heels
for Young Chae,

216
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:55,990
you're betraying Ha Neul
to side with Jin Se Hoon?

217
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,800
I wasn't thinking straight.

218
00:10:57,930 --> 00:10:59,560
You should oust
Chairman Han Hye Ra...

219
00:10:59,830 --> 00:11:02,330
and make Joo Ha Neul
the new chairman.

220
00:11:02,330 --> 00:11:03,330
That's the right move.

221
00:11:10,540 --> 00:11:12,440
As long as Han Hye Ra
remains the chairman,

222
00:11:12,810 --> 00:11:14,550
it will be impossible
to reform Kunhyang Group.

223
00:11:14,610 --> 00:11:17,210
That's right.
Regarding corporate management,

224
00:11:17,280 --> 00:11:19,780
she has failed to fulfill
her ethical responsibilities.

225
00:11:19,850 --> 00:11:23,390
Investors, the financial sector,
the Fair Trade Commission,

226
00:11:23,390 --> 00:11:24,460
and our clients have warned us
about her leadership.

227
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:26,220
And they're demanding a review
of their relationship with us.

228
00:11:26,560 --> 00:11:30,730
As a result, we're about to lose
our contracts with global partners.

229
00:11:31,600 --> 00:11:33,530
This is a total mess.

230
00:11:34,030 --> 00:11:35,530
To save Kunhyang,

231
00:11:36,030 --> 00:11:37,030
- We have no choice...
- we have no choice...

232
00:11:37,030 --> 00:11:38,040
- but to replace the chairman.
- but to replace the chairman.

233
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:40,040
That will be our only option.

234
00:11:52,520 --> 00:11:54,390
The board is starting
to make its move.

235
00:11:54,750 --> 00:11:57,760
A motion to replace the chairman
will be on the agenda soon.

236
00:11:58,990 --> 00:12:00,060
Did you do it?

237
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:04,030
I reached out and convinced them.

238
00:12:04,230 --> 00:12:05,800
Does Chairman Han know about this?

239
00:12:06,560 --> 00:12:08,030
It's what my mother wants.

240
00:12:08,030 --> 00:12:09,670
I have to take her down myself...

241
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:12,070
so that Jin Tae Seok
will trust me completely.

242
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:16,410
Jin Tae Seok will think
I'm just following his orders.

243
00:12:16,470 --> 00:12:19,080
- The fool.
- We'll still need a good reason.

244
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:27,150
A reason? We can always make one up.

245
00:12:28,490 --> 00:12:32,320
While I was chairman, my husband,
the Honorary Chairman Jin Tae Seok,

246
00:12:33,320 --> 00:12:35,460
confessed to a major crime.

247
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:37,900
It caused a huge public backlash...

248
00:12:37,960 --> 00:12:41,800
And it dealt a fatal blow
to the company's image and trust?

249
00:12:41,870 --> 00:12:44,570
Civic groups
have even started boycotts.

250
00:12:44,700 --> 00:12:46,640
But it's not your fault.

251
00:12:46,840 --> 00:12:50,010
You had no idea that Jin Tae Seok
was such a monster.

252
00:12:50,110 --> 00:12:53,080
I can't just claim ignorance
or call it a personal matter.

253
00:12:53,840 --> 00:12:55,650
If I didn't know,
the board will think I'm incompetent,

254
00:12:55,650 --> 00:12:57,750
and if I did,
they'll think I was an accomplice...

255
00:12:57,820 --> 00:12:59,320
or that I covered it up.

256
00:12:59,380 --> 00:13:01,250
You want me to lead that charge?

257
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,520
Right now,

258
00:13:03,450 --> 00:13:06,620
that's your job, Jung Won.
The Vice Chairman will help you.

259
00:13:07,730 --> 00:13:08,760
Ma'am, but...

260
00:13:09,330 --> 00:13:10,560
Jin Tae Seok...

261
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:12,830
Let's start by
inflating his ego even more.

262
00:13:13,230 --> 00:13:14,330
That's our goal.

263
00:13:14,330 --> 00:13:15,570
And what about Chairman Gong?

264
00:13:16,130 --> 00:13:18,570
- What do you think she'll do?
- It's hard to say.

265
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:21,940
She's such a loose cannon.

266
00:13:30,510 --> 00:13:33,380
Then who do you intend
to name as the new chairman?

267
00:13:33,650 --> 00:13:36,550
Vice President Jin Se Hoon
has to be the next chairman.

268
00:13:37,520 --> 00:13:39,090
But there's already a vice chairman.

269
00:13:39,220 --> 00:13:40,490
Is that even possible?

270
00:13:42,760 --> 00:13:44,160
Goodness.

271
00:13:44,830 --> 00:13:48,070
Of course,
that's out of the question.

272
00:13:51,370 --> 00:13:53,770
I support ousting Chairman Han.

273
00:13:53,770 --> 00:13:55,810
As for the next chairman,

274
00:13:55,870 --> 00:13:58,810
I'm perfectly fine with recommending
Vice President Jin Se Hoon.

275
00:14:11,520 --> 00:14:13,360
The board said they wanted to make
Vice President Jin Se Hoon...

276
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,530
the chairman?

277
00:14:16,430 --> 00:14:17,930
And Chairman Gong, too?

278
00:14:19,300 --> 00:14:21,570
I thought she was going
to back Ha Neul.

279
00:14:21,930 --> 00:14:25,170
Do you think Jin Tae Seok
got to Chairman Gong?

280
00:14:25,900 --> 00:14:28,370
The way things are going,
Vice President Jin Se Hoon...

281
00:14:28,370 --> 00:14:29,840
will become chairman soon.

282
00:14:29,910 --> 00:14:32,110
If that happens,
Jin Tae Seok will make a comeback.

283
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:34,950
He'll be pulling Se Hoon's strings
from the shadows.

284
00:14:35,610 --> 00:14:37,580
We have to stop him,
no matter what it takes.

285
00:14:44,290 --> 00:14:45,590
Designer Joo Young Chae.

286
00:14:46,020 --> 00:14:49,260
You have tarnished the reputation
of the Kunhyang Group's Design Team.

287
00:14:49,790 --> 00:14:52,900
- You're aware of that, aren't you?
- As if I'm the only one.

288
00:14:53,430 --> 00:14:54,770
What I did is nothing in comparison.

289
00:14:55,730 --> 00:14:58,940
- Right?
- Well, you still don't get it.

290
00:14:59,040 --> 00:15:00,640
I think she's lost her mind.

291
00:15:01,010 --> 00:15:03,770
Designer Joo Young Chae, get a grip.

292
00:15:04,210 --> 00:15:06,910
Your long-standing habit
of stealing other people's designs.

293
00:15:07,010 --> 00:15:08,250
That's the problem.

294
00:15:08,780 --> 00:15:10,450
This is all your fault!

295
00:15:10,650 --> 00:15:12,980
You're a nobody,
but you're more talented than I am.

296
00:15:13,050 --> 00:15:14,420
That's the biggest problem of all!

297
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:15,490
Enough!

298
00:15:15,820 --> 00:15:17,350
After thorough deliberation,

299
00:15:17,350 --> 00:15:19,820
the board members
of Kunhyang Group have decided.

300
00:15:20,390 --> 00:15:21,430
I'll inform you of it now.

301
00:15:22,460 --> 00:15:24,430
Se Hoon will protect me.

302
00:15:24,960 --> 00:15:26,560
Nothing's going to happen to me.

303
00:15:26,860 --> 00:15:28,100
Joo Young Chae,

304
00:15:28,670 --> 00:15:30,970
effective today, you are fired.

305
00:15:32,640 --> 00:15:33,640
What?

306
00:15:38,210 --> 00:15:39,210
Fired?

307
00:15:40,810 --> 00:15:42,410
Who dares fire me?

308
00:15:43,380 --> 00:15:45,780
- Who?
- Pack your things and leave now.

309
00:15:45,850 --> 00:15:47,820
Do you know who I am?
How dare you treat me this way?

310
00:15:48,250 --> 00:15:51,890
Kunhyang Group is mine!
It belongs to me, Joo Young Chae!

311
00:16:07,670 --> 00:16:09,270
How did my life come to this?

312
00:16:10,310 --> 00:16:11,640
I didn't do anything wrong.

313
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,010
That's right.

314
00:16:15,180 --> 00:16:16,610
It's all Cha Jung Won's fault.

315
00:16:18,050 --> 00:16:19,780
Cha Jung Won did this to me.

316
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:32,400
Where can I even go like this?

317
00:16:42,940 --> 00:16:45,010
She looks like
she hasn't eaten in weeks.

318
00:16:46,110 --> 00:16:48,650
- Don't tell me...
- Maybe she came to you...

319
00:16:48,980 --> 00:16:50,150
to get revenge...

320
00:16:50,210 --> 00:16:51,650
after getting fired
from the Design Team?

321
00:16:52,850 --> 00:16:55,450
Forget revenge.
Something's off about her.

322
00:16:55,950 --> 00:16:57,250
I think she's pregnant.

323
00:16:58,290 --> 00:17:00,360
Given how she's wolfing down
all that meat,

324
00:17:00,620 --> 00:17:01,960
it must be a boy.

325
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,260
No way...

326
00:17:04,190 --> 00:17:05,430
No, that can't be it.

327
00:17:06,630 --> 00:17:08,700
She already pulled
that fake pregnancy stunt.

328
00:17:09,100 --> 00:17:11,640
I hope she's not.

329
00:17:13,340 --> 00:17:14,770
Can I get another plate of meat?

330
00:17:15,940 --> 00:17:18,080
Use the kiosk. That's how you order.

331
00:17:24,850 --> 00:17:27,650
This is weird. Where is it?

332
00:17:27,790 --> 00:17:29,150
You forgot your wallet, right?

333
00:17:30,590 --> 00:17:33,560
But I'm sure
I placed the order already.

334
00:17:33,620 --> 00:17:34,760
That was on the house.

335
00:17:35,330 --> 00:17:39,530
I'll give you another plate on me,
so eat up and stay out of trouble.

336
00:17:39,800 --> 00:17:40,800
Part-Timer Hwang.

337
00:17:40,930 --> 00:17:42,930
(Damga Charcoal Grill)

338
00:17:48,110 --> 00:17:49,310
Enjoy your meal.

339
00:17:50,270 --> 00:17:51,580
Just put it on my tab.

340
00:17:51,580 --> 00:17:54,550
Sure. Or you can work it off.

341
00:17:55,910 --> 00:17:58,220
You want me to work here?

342
00:18:00,920 --> 00:18:02,690
This is my second job, too.

343
00:18:03,420 --> 00:18:04,560
It's fun.

344
00:18:05,190 --> 00:18:06,420
It's so annoying already,

345
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:09,790
so just don't get in my way
while I'm eating.

346
00:18:27,510 --> 00:18:29,480
The colors and the graphics
aren't my style.

347
00:18:31,550 --> 00:18:32,880
I'll just give this to Jung Won.

348
00:18:34,590 --> 00:18:35,650
Jung Won would be grateful...

349
00:18:36,220 --> 00:18:38,690
for whatever I give,
even my hand-me-downs.

350
00:18:41,330 --> 00:18:43,290
(Kunhyang Group)

351
00:18:44,190 --> 00:18:48,530
The fashion show was disappointing,
but the launch must go smoothly.

352
00:18:49,330 --> 00:18:51,200
We need to start by checking
the production lines...

353
00:18:53,100 --> 00:18:54,100
Team Leader Cha?

354
00:18:56,670 --> 00:18:58,180
What's on your mind?

355
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,880
Are you worried
about the board meeting?

356
00:19:01,610 --> 00:19:03,210
Is the chairman really
changing again?

357
00:19:03,710 --> 00:19:06,220
The whole office is buzzing
about it.

358
00:19:07,080 --> 00:19:08,850
I'm not sure.

359
00:19:09,990 --> 00:19:11,990
What do you think, Team Leader Cha?

360
00:19:13,260 --> 00:19:14,760
Things will unfold
as they're meant to.

361
00:19:20,760 --> 00:19:23,170
Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul
and Vice President Jin Se Hoon,

362
00:19:23,470 --> 00:19:26,740
regarding the motion to appoint
one of them as the new chairman,

363
00:19:27,140 --> 00:19:28,810
we will now vote by a show of hands.

364
00:19:29,440 --> 00:19:32,380
Eight of the 13 board members
are present.

365
00:19:32,880 --> 00:19:35,380
Vice President Jin Se Hoon
and Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul...

366
00:19:35,380 --> 00:19:36,710
will not be voting.

367
00:19:37,250 --> 00:19:40,950
The five absent members have already
cast their votes online.

368
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:43,520
First,
for Vice President Jin Se Hoon.

369
00:19:44,420 --> 00:19:46,920
All in favor,
please raise your hands.

370
00:20:08,850 --> 00:20:09,850
Next,

371
00:20:09,850 --> 00:20:11,110
all those in favor...

372
00:20:11,110 --> 00:20:12,850
of Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul
as the next Chairman,

373
00:20:13,520 --> 00:20:14,650
please raise your hands.

374
00:20:16,890 --> 00:20:18,120
I'm in favor.

375
00:20:19,920 --> 00:20:20,920
Chairman Gong.

376
00:20:22,360 --> 00:20:23,360
I second the motion.

377
00:20:26,430 --> 00:20:27,430
I abstain.

378
00:20:38,610 --> 00:20:40,440
The vote from those present
is two to three.

379
00:20:40,940 --> 00:20:43,780
And after tallying the early votes,

380
00:20:44,250 --> 00:20:45,880
out of 13 total board members,

381
00:20:46,450 --> 00:20:50,350
excluding Joo Ha Neul, Jin Se Hoon,
and Cha Jung Won who abstained,

382
00:20:50,690 --> 00:20:52,090
seven out of the ten
remaining voters...

383
00:20:52,620 --> 00:20:55,390
voted for a single candidate.

384
00:20:56,290 --> 00:20:57,330
The next chairman is...

385
00:21:01,870 --> 00:21:03,100
Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul.

386
00:21:11,640 --> 00:21:12,640
Congratulations.

387
00:21:17,780 --> 00:21:18,780
Thank you.

388
00:21:19,420 --> 00:21:20,850
I will do my best
to fulfill my duties.

389
00:21:22,090 --> 00:21:23,690
Many congrats!

390
00:21:27,660 --> 00:21:29,290
Joo Ha Neul.

391
00:21:29,290 --> 00:21:31,130
When did he win over
the board members?

392
00:21:32,860 --> 00:21:35,430
We have a personnel announcement
regarding the election results.

393
00:21:36,270 --> 00:21:37,900
We appoint
Vice President Jin Se Hoon...

394
00:21:37,900 --> 00:21:40,300
as the group's new vice chairman.

395
00:21:59,060 --> 00:22:02,560
How did the board find out
you're not my biological son?

396
00:22:03,130 --> 00:22:04,430
Joo Ha Neul must have told them.

397
00:22:04,660 --> 00:22:07,000
Even Gong Nan Sook stabbed you
in the back at the last minute.

398
00:22:07,300 --> 00:22:08,700
That just goes to show
what you're made of.

399
00:22:14,340 --> 00:22:17,040
Joo Ha Neul,
how dare you take what's mine?

400
00:22:18,410 --> 00:22:19,610
Me? Just the vice chairman?

401
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:22,210
I have to answer to Joo Ha Neul?

402
00:22:23,310 --> 00:22:24,550
Why?

403
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:32,520
You seem thrilled.

404
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:34,220
Is it because your son
is Kunhyang's new chairman?

405
00:22:35,690 --> 00:22:37,160
Hey, I'm so happy I could just die.

406
00:22:38,030 --> 00:22:39,830
I just can't stop laughing.

407
00:22:40,930 --> 00:22:41,930
There's something
I've been wondering.

408
00:22:42,970 --> 00:22:44,270
What is it? Ask away.

409
00:22:45,570 --> 00:22:49,170
I knew you backed Vice Chairman Joo,
I mean, Chairman Joo Ha Neul,

410
00:22:49,640 --> 00:22:51,170
I thought you'd recommend...

411
00:22:51,170 --> 00:22:53,780
Vice President Jin Se Hoon
for chairman...

412
00:22:53,880 --> 00:22:56,350
That was just for show.

413
00:22:58,380 --> 00:23:01,080
Why did you call me out
at this hour?

414
00:23:01,350 --> 00:23:03,650
It's fitting for you,
don't you think, Gong Nan Sook?

415
00:23:04,420 --> 00:23:05,420
The Chairman in the shadow.

416
00:23:06,120 --> 00:23:09,260
True. They used to call me
the Night-Blooming Rose.

417
00:23:09,690 --> 00:23:11,190
Okay, let's get down to business.

418
00:23:11,190 --> 00:23:14,630
What must Light and Shadow agree on?

419
00:23:17,030 --> 00:23:19,400
I'm stepping down as chairman soon.

420
00:23:20,340 --> 00:23:22,610
If you step down,
am I out automatically too?

421
00:23:23,140 --> 00:23:26,910
Hey, why don't you ask me
if I want to stay on or not?

422
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:29,510
Thinking about it makes me angry.

423
00:23:29,510 --> 00:23:32,180
It's a fake-out for Jin Tae Seok.

424
00:23:33,980 --> 00:23:34,990
A fake-out?

425
00:23:35,820 --> 00:23:38,360
That's my kind of thing.
This'll be fun.

426
00:23:38,490 --> 00:23:42,330
So we'll deceive him
with a trick, right?

427
00:23:42,690 --> 00:23:45,660
So all we have to do is
make Jin Tae Seok buy it, right?

428
00:23:47,260 --> 00:23:50,500
The problem is who's going to be
the next chairman.

429
00:23:50,670 --> 00:23:53,570
That just depends on
the board members.

430
00:23:54,040 --> 00:23:55,340
I heard Cha Jung Won
is spearheading this?

431
00:23:55,570 --> 00:23:58,070
Jung Won took the lead
in ousting me.

432
00:23:58,410 --> 00:24:00,240
She's pretending to be
Jin Tae Seok's attack dog.

433
00:24:01,950 --> 00:24:03,280
So she's not in a position
to be considered...

434
00:24:03,280 --> 00:24:04,380
for the next chairman.

435
00:24:05,220 --> 00:24:08,050
Jin Tae Seok will obviously
push for Jin Se Hoon.

436
00:24:08,320 --> 00:24:11,050
He'll be looking for an opening
to make a comeback,

437
00:24:11,120 --> 00:24:14,120
so he'll use Se Hoon to do it.

438
00:24:15,190 --> 00:24:18,560
I want to put Joo Ha Neul
in the chairman's seat.

439
00:24:19,830 --> 00:24:21,030
Not Cha Jung Won?

440
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:25,500
There's a proper order to things.
As for Jung Won,

441
00:24:25,840 --> 00:24:29,410
she needs more time
to gain Jin Tae Seok's trust.

442
00:24:29,970 --> 00:24:31,110
Okay.

443
00:24:31,110 --> 00:24:34,140
So at first,
I'll pretend to back Jin Se Hoon,

444
00:24:34,480 --> 00:24:36,680
then, at the last minute,
along with the board members,

445
00:24:36,750 --> 00:24:39,550
I'll turn the tables on the vote.
That's the plan, right?

446
00:24:40,220 --> 00:24:41,380
This is going to be so much fun.

447
00:24:42,390 --> 00:24:43,450
A fake-out...

448
00:24:47,790 --> 00:24:49,860
And that's how it all went down.

449
00:24:52,860 --> 00:24:54,530
Hey, close your mouth.
You'll catch flies.

450
00:24:55,130 --> 00:24:56,530
My goodness.

451
00:24:56,530 --> 00:24:59,900
That's a tactic straight out of
the Records of the Three Kingdoms.

452
00:25:00,170 --> 00:25:01,970
Respect to you two iron ladies.

453
00:25:03,270 --> 00:25:06,380
From now on, you can call me
"Gong the Glorious." Got it?

454
00:25:08,750 --> 00:25:10,950
I'm so happy I could just die.

455
00:25:19,560 --> 00:25:24,230
(Chairman Joo Ha Neul)

456
00:25:24,530 --> 00:25:26,430
You made it. Vice Chair...

457
00:25:27,330 --> 00:25:29,000
No, I mean Chairman Joo.

458
00:25:29,830 --> 00:25:32,040
I don't know if I'm up to the task.

459
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:34,140
You'll do a better job than I did.
I have no doubt.

460
00:25:35,240 --> 00:25:37,940
I wouldn't have given this to you
if I weren't certain.

461
00:25:39,210 --> 00:25:41,650
Congratulations,
Chairman Joo Ha Neul.

462
00:25:42,580 --> 00:25:43,580
Thank you.

463
00:25:49,750 --> 00:25:51,120
We've cleared one hurdle.

464
00:25:52,720 --> 00:25:54,690
Once Chairman Joo
is officially inaugurated,

465
00:25:55,960 --> 00:25:58,560
they're bound to strike back.

466
00:25:59,000 --> 00:26:00,230
I'm prepared for it.

467
00:26:00,300 --> 00:26:02,600
We have to be prepared
for whatever they throw at us.

468
00:26:03,770 --> 00:26:05,770
Doesn't Jin Tae Seok
suspect anything?

469
00:26:06,300 --> 00:26:09,170
- Not yet.
- Or he might know and is faking it.

470
00:26:10,310 --> 00:26:11,640
I'll go meet with him myself.

471
00:26:13,140 --> 00:26:14,140
Alone?

472
00:26:28,760 --> 00:26:29,990
What in the world are you wearing?

473
00:26:30,930 --> 00:26:33,300
It's the latest style from New York.
Isn't it fabulous?

474
00:26:35,630 --> 00:26:36,630
I feel unsettled.

475
00:26:36,630 --> 00:26:39,900
My head is about to explode already,
so please, just leave.

476
00:26:40,040 --> 00:26:43,310
But why are you in Ha Neul's office?

477
00:26:44,870 --> 00:26:46,040
You should be in
the chairman's office.

478
00:26:47,140 --> 00:26:49,480
- You're the chairman.
- Are you trying to rub it in?

479
00:26:49,850 --> 00:26:52,620
Joo Ha Neul is the chairman now.
I'm the vice chairman.

480
00:26:52,880 --> 00:26:54,250
You came here
without even knowing that?

481
00:26:57,150 --> 00:26:58,150
Joo Young Chae.

482
00:26:59,190 --> 00:27:00,460
Did you know about this all along?

483
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,960
- Know what?
- About your mother.

484
00:27:03,630 --> 00:27:05,230
She said she'd make me the chairman,

485
00:27:05,800 --> 00:27:06,930
but she turned on me
at the last minute.

486
00:27:08,530 --> 00:27:11,970
Did you and Joo Ha Neul team up
with her just to screw me over?

487
00:27:14,470 --> 00:27:15,470
It's true.

488
00:27:19,540 --> 00:27:21,580
My mother only ever adored Ha Neul.

489
00:27:22,150 --> 00:27:25,520
He was athletic, a good student,
kind-hearted, and honest.

490
00:27:27,380 --> 00:27:29,490
She must've wondered how a son
like him ever came into her life.

491
00:27:29,820 --> 00:27:30,890
It was probably like
a godsend to her.

492
00:27:31,860 --> 00:27:33,090
And I was the problem child.

493
00:27:33,360 --> 00:27:36,990
How could she love her adopted son
more than her own daughter?

494
00:27:37,160 --> 00:27:39,900
When Ha Neul got his report card,
we'd go out for a nice dinner.

495
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:42,100
She'd rip mine up on the spot.

496
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:45,600
So Ha Neul's the chairman now.

497
00:27:46,670 --> 00:27:48,200
Madam Gong must be over the moon.

498
00:27:52,840 --> 00:27:55,780
I'm going to be thrown
in the bathtub again.

499
00:27:57,780 --> 00:28:01,950
Se Hoon, please hide me.
I don't want drown.

500
00:28:02,220 --> 00:28:03,420
Please hide me.

501
00:28:05,060 --> 00:28:06,060
Young Chae.

502
00:28:06,660 --> 00:28:07,660
Young Chae.

503
00:28:08,290 --> 00:28:09,860
Young Chae, snap out of it!

504
00:28:09,860 --> 00:28:10,890
Hey!

505
00:28:18,330 --> 00:28:19,600
I'm fine.

506
00:28:21,070 --> 00:28:22,340
I should get going.

507
00:28:32,150 --> 00:28:33,980
(Kunhyang Group)

508
00:28:44,190 --> 00:28:45,200
What's up with her outfit?

509
00:28:47,700 --> 00:28:48,700
Joo Young Chae.

510
00:28:52,970 --> 00:28:54,170
Are you sleepwalking or something?

511
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:56,610
What are you doing here?
You were fired.

512
00:28:56,770 --> 00:28:57,770
Do I know you?

513
00:28:58,980 --> 00:29:01,040
- Hey, you're my sister-in-law.
- "Sister-in-law?"

514
00:29:02,550 --> 00:29:03,980
I don't have a sister-in-law.

515
00:29:05,150 --> 00:29:06,150
How annoying.

516
00:29:08,420 --> 00:29:09,420
What's wrong with her?

517
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:11,550
Has she lost her mind?

518
00:29:25,970 --> 00:29:27,200
All those in favor...

519
00:29:27,200 --> 00:29:29,340
of Vice Chairman Joo Ha Neul
as the next Chairman,

520
00:29:29,670 --> 00:29:30,740
please raise your hands.

521
00:29:31,710 --> 00:29:32,710
I abstain.

522
00:29:36,080 --> 00:29:38,310
Well done. On half of it, anyway.

523
00:29:40,050 --> 00:29:41,820
And here I thought
I'd get a perfect score.

524
00:29:42,320 --> 00:29:43,590
Only 50 out of 100?

525
00:29:43,690 --> 00:29:45,420
Se Hoon should've
been made chairman.

526
00:29:46,060 --> 00:29:47,520
You should have made that happen.

527
00:29:47,660 --> 00:29:50,660
How was I supposed to do
what even you couldn't, Father?

528
00:29:50,860 --> 00:29:52,430
Se Hoon has to be the chairman...

529
00:29:53,230 --> 00:29:55,500
for me to control Kunhyang
as I please.

530
00:29:57,630 --> 00:29:59,440
Or, as a long shot,

531
00:30:01,070 --> 00:30:02,840
you could have made me the chairman.

532
00:30:03,640 --> 00:30:04,770
So you could control me more easily.

533
00:30:05,410 --> 00:30:06,410
What?

534
00:30:11,580 --> 00:30:12,850
Yes. That's the spirit.

535
00:30:13,750 --> 00:30:14,950
That's my girl.

536
00:30:15,390 --> 00:30:16,390
Didn't you know?

537
00:30:16,920 --> 00:30:19,760
Han Hye Ra, who gave up her life
for her ambition.

538
00:30:20,290 --> 00:30:22,460
And you, who tried to kill me,
knowing I was your own daughter.

539
00:30:23,330 --> 00:30:25,360
I am the monster you both created.

540
00:30:26,530 --> 00:30:27,530
Exactly.

541
00:30:27,860 --> 00:30:29,930
I've already cut away
all my emotions.

542
00:30:31,230 --> 00:30:33,270
From now on, to get what I want,

543
00:30:33,800 --> 00:30:35,640
I will be relentless
in forging my own path.

544
00:30:37,310 --> 00:30:39,040
So you'd even take out Joo Ha Neul?

545
00:30:43,310 --> 00:30:44,650
If that's what it takes.

546
00:30:45,980 --> 00:30:48,890
Weren't you and Joo Ha Neul lovers?

547
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:54,420
It seemed like Joo Ha Neul
would die for you.

548
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:04,270
I even cast out the mother
who abandoned me.

549
00:31:05,340 --> 00:31:08,040
I don't need pathetic things
like love.

550
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:11,010
Not if it gets in the way
of becoming Kunhyang's chairman.

551
00:31:11,410 --> 00:31:14,210
With that attitude, I bet you could
even stab me in the back.

552
00:31:14,280 --> 00:31:15,310
Isn't that a given?

553
00:31:16,410 --> 00:31:19,880
You tried to kill me two,
even three times, Father.

554
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:24,420
Are you scared?

555
00:31:25,690 --> 00:31:28,760
For a small fry,
you're not just audacious,

556
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:31,190
and you've got some serious gall.

557
00:31:31,290 --> 00:31:34,530
You should have nipped it in the bud
when you had the chance.

558
00:31:35,770 --> 00:31:37,700
- Unless...
- Unless what?

559
00:31:39,440 --> 00:31:42,110
You have no other cards to play,
Father.

560
00:31:43,110 --> 00:31:44,670
Se Mi is too weak,

561
00:31:45,380 --> 00:31:47,410
Se Hoon isn't your blood,

562
00:31:48,080 --> 00:31:49,950
and he even turned on you.

563
00:31:51,510 --> 00:31:54,720
So accept me as your own
and your heir...

564
00:31:55,450 --> 00:31:56,890
sincerely.

565
00:31:59,260 --> 00:32:01,360
You should start
by making me believe you.

566
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:18,510
(A Graceful Liar)

567
00:32:41,830 --> 00:32:43,870
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
